      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<div class=\"item-attunement\"><i>(Requires attunement by a Spellcaster)</i></div><p>This wand has 7 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges to cast the <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.2jr9gocEUofHEZ0B]{polymorph} spell (save DC 15) from it.</p>\n<p>The wand regains 1d6 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the wand crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.</p>\n</div>",
